# Task Management Guidelines

- **Task Breakdown:**  
  - Divide work into clear, manageable tasks using the MECE (Mutually Exclusive, Collectively Exhaustive) approach.
- **Documentation:**  
  - Update @notes/task_list.md and @notes/conversation_summary.md regularly to record progress.
- **Prioritization:**  
  - Prioritize tasks based on project goals and deadlines.
- **Review:**  
  - Regularly review progress and adjust plans as necessary.
